  <brief_title>Management of Highly Active Anti-retroviral Therapy-related Hyperlipidemia Among HIV-infected Patients in Taiwan</brief_title>
  <official_title>Tropical Medicine Center (TMC), Kaohsiung Medicine University Hospital (KMUH)</official_title>
